Package: sofamatic
Type: Package
Title: Sequential Organ Failure Assessment (SOFA) Scoring in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given  = "Keano",
                  family = "Samaritakis",
                  role   = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                  email  = "do-not-contact@invalid",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6338-1918"))
Description: Vectorised, dependency-light functions to compute Sequential
    Organ Failure Assessment (SOFA) sub-scores and the total SOFA score
    from clinical data, including longitudinal helpers for first-day and
    worst-day scoring per subject. Supports SI and conventional units for
    PaO2/FiO2, bilirubin, and creatinine, and offers configurable handling
    of missing Glasgow Coma Scale values in sedated and non-sedated
    patients. Methodology follows Vincent et al. (1996)
    <doi:10.1007/BF01709751>.
